    "History": {
      "rows": [
        [
          "Staff Generated History",
          "",
          "Created By:",
          "TS"
        ],
        [
          "You were born in the Hungarian Mountains almost two centuries ago.  Your family is a good family, you serve your masters, and do the things they can not do for themselves.  You came to the Americas in the late 1800's part of the wave of immigrants, but you came with a purpose not just your own.  You brought your family with you.  You brought three breeders and four young Revenants, you would make your masters happy and proud of your actions.  You found you and yours in the LA area within a few years and have been here ever since.  You settled and let the breeders do their thing.  You have been throwing amazing parties doing amazing drugs and fucking anything that moves since.  The best part is it is in the service of the Masters.  Admittedly your becoming a bit jaded, I mean you crave it, but something had/has to change and well oh boy did it.  The house in West Adams you were staying at was attacked by a vampire, you and your family members were able to determine you think its a camarilla member.  You have his photo.  He took the most precious thing from your family.  You had Zantosa/Grimaldi/Dahabi crossbreed babies and were working on raising a whole new line to serve the masters and that fuck stole them.  You found out that Szymon was going to be attending one of the Camarilla gatherings and you and the house mother practically begged and demanded to attend him, to find out who you have to kill and how to get them back."
